                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Body protection: Safety vests, coveralls, high-visibility clothing"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Foot protection: Steel-toe boots, slip-resistant shoes, chemical boots"
