          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Centralized Procurement Strategy"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Consolidate MRO purchasing to leverage volume discounts and simplify supplier management. Many companies save 15-25% by centralizing their MRO procurement."
